**Barber** | Townsfolk Killing
__Basics__
Once per game, the Barber may choose to immediately attack one player during the day.
__Details__
After Day 1, at any time during the day, the Barber may once attack another player. 
The Barber also receives the choice whether they want to be revealed or not. If they choose to be revealed both their role and name is announced, otherwise neither is.
The Barberâ€™s attack is an immediate ability.
